1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,040
Hello, English learners.
你好，英语学习者。

2
00:00:03,040 --> 00:00:04,440
Welcome back to EnglishPod.
欢迎回到EnglishPod。

3
00:00:04,440 --> 00:00:05,440
My name is Marco.
我叫Marco。

4
00:00:05,440 --> 00:00:06,440
And I'm Erika.
我是Erika。

5
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:11,280
And today we're bringing you another great lesson about sports, part of our sports series.
今天我们要给你们带来另一节关于体育的精彩课程，这是我们体育系列的一部分。

6
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:12,280
That's right.
没错。

7
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:18,200
And in this lesson, we are talking about maybe the world's most favorite sport.
在这节课中，我们要谈论的可能是全世界最受欢迎的体育运动。

8
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:19,200
Right.
对。

9
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:23,000
One of the most popular sports in the world, soccer.
世界上最受欢迎的运动之一，足球。

10
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:25,320
Or also known as football in other countries.
在其他国家也被称为football。

11
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,320
Yes.
是的。

12
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:30,840
So, before we get started with this great lesson, let's take a look at some of the words
那么，在我们开始这节精彩的课程之前，让我们先看一下词汇预览中对话里会出现的一些单词。

13
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:35,280
we'll find in the dialogue in Vocabulary Preview.
词汇预览。

14
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,040
Vocabulary Preview.
词汇预览。

15
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:39,340
We're going to look at three words here.
我们要看三个词。

16
00:00:39,340 --> 00:00:42,720
The first word is wingman.
第一个词是wingman。

17
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:43,720
Wingman.
Wingman。

18
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:44,720
A wingman.
一个wingman。

19
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:48,720
Now, wingman isn't really related to soccer in any way.
嗯，wingman其实和足球没什么关系。

20
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:49,720
Okay.
好的。

21
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:53,500
But it's a way of referring to somebody as your right hand.
但它是一种称呼某人为你得力助手的方式。

22
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:55,080
So your helper.
也就是你的帮手。

23
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,280
Your helper.
你的帮手。

24
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,760
Your number one guy.
你的头号人物。

25
00:00:57,760 --> 00:00:58,760
Okay.
好的。

26
00:00:58,760 --> 00:00:59,760
Right.
对。

27
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:02,880
So a wingman is someone who helps you a lot.
所以wingman就是那个帮你很多忙的人。

28
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:03,880
Exactly.
没错。

29
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:04,880
Okay.
好的。

30
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:06,880
Our next word, tied.
下一个词，tied。

31
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:08,360
Tied.
Tied。

32
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:10,080
They are tied.
他们打平了。

33
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,080
They are tied.
他们打平了。

34
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:18,360
Now, this is an interesting word because tie can be a noun, verb, and an adjective, right?
这个词很有意思，因为tie可以是名词、动词，还有形容词，对吧？

35
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,360
Exactly.
没错。

36
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,900
So in this case, they are tied.
所以在这里，they are tied。

37
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:22,880
It's an adjective meaning...
它是一个形容词，意思是……

38
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:24,440
They have the same score.
他们得分相同。

39
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,440
Okay.
好的。

40
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:27,520
So a tie is...
所以tie就是……

41
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:31,080
Is a game that has ended with no winner or loser.
一场没有赢家或输家的比赛。

42
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,600
Both of them had the same score.
双方得分相同。

43
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:33,600
Exactly.
没错。

44
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:39,520
And so obviously, the verb to tie is to reach the same score as your other team.
那么很明显，动词to tie就是和对方球队达到相同得分。

45
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,520
Exactly.
没错。

46
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,520
All right.
好的。

47
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:46,920
Well, our third word can also be used as a noun and a verb and it is foul.
嗯，我们的第三个词也可以用作名词和动词，它就是foul。

48
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,920
Fouled.
Fouled。

49
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,920
Fouled.
Fouled。

50
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,920
Okay.
好的。

51
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:57,760
So, to foul somebody is to do something to them that is not allowed in the sport.
所以，to foul somebody就是在运动中对他们做不被允许的事情。

52
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,880
Okay.
好的。

53
00:01:58,880 --> 00:02:02,560
And so when you do this, you have committed a foul.
当你这样做时，你就犯了一个foul（犯规）。

54
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,560
Exactly.
没错。

55
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,560
Okay.
好的。

56
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:07,280
So you use it in the same way, to foul or a foul.
所以用法是一样的，to foul或a foul。

57
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,280
Interesting.
有意思。

58
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:12,160
Well, we're going to hear these three words in context now.
嗯，我们现在要在上下文中听到这三个词了。

59
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:29,880
So why don't we listen to our soccer dialogue?
那我们为什么不听听我们的足球对话呢？

60
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:30,960
Welcome back, soccer fans.
欢迎回来，球迷们。

61
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,160
My name is Rick Fields.
我是Rick Fields。

62
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:35,680
And as always, I am joined by my commentating wingman, Bob Copeland.
和往常一样，我的解说搭档Bob Copeland也在这里。

63
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:41,340
And we're in the brink of soccer history today as Ecuador and Brazil are tied 1-1.
今天我们正处在足球历史的边缘，厄瓜多尔和巴西1-1打平。

64
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:46,520
As we begin the second half of the 2022 World Cup.
2022年世界杯下半场开始了。

65
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,080
The ref calls the players for the kickoff.
裁判叫球员们准备开球。

66
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,720
And here we go.
比赛开始了。

67
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,720
Ecuador quickly passes the ball to the midfield.
厄瓜多尔迅速将球传到中场。

68
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,440
But oh, it's out of bounds.
但是哦，球出界了。

69
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,920
That'll be a throw in for Brazil.
巴西队获得一个界外球。

70
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:58,980
Adriano has the ball and makes a long pass to Robinho.
Adriano拿到球，长传给Robinho。

71
00:02:58,980 --> 00:03:00,760
And the ref has called him offside.
裁判判他越位。

72
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:01,800
No question about it.
毫无疑问。

73
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,640
He was offside by a mile.
他越位了一大截。

74
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:05,200
We have a goal kick for Ecuador.
厄瓜多尔队获得一个球门球。

75
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,000
Edison Mendes heads it to Valencia.
Edison Mendes头球传给Valencia。

76
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,000
He shoots.
他射门了。

77
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,000
Deflected by the defender.
被后卫挡出。

78
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,840
And we have a corner kick.
我们得到一个角球。

79
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,280
Delgado takes the corner.
Delgado主罚角球。

80
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,280
We have a foul.
犯规了。

81
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,280
Oh no.
哦不。

82
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:17,760
Dida, the goalkeeper, has fouled the Ecuadorian player.
守门员Dida对厄瓜多尔球员犯规了。

83
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,760
He gets a yellow card.
他得到一张黄牌。

84
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:21,120
And that will be a penalty kick.
那将是一个点球。

85
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:24,640
This is the perfect opportunity for Ecuador to get ahead in this match and become world
这是厄瓜多尔在这场比赛中取得领先并成为世界冠军的绝佳机会。

86
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,640
champions.
冠军。

87
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:26,880
He gets ready for the kick.
他准备罚球。

88
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,880
He shoots.
他射门了。

89
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:28,880
And he...
他……

90
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:45,240
OK, so Ecuador tied with Brazil in the 2022 World Cup.
好的，所以厄瓜多尔在2022年世界杯上与巴西打平了。

91
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:50,760
Wow, Marco, I'm really happy to see that you are able to see so far into the future.
哇，Marco，我很高兴看到你能预见那么远的未来。

92
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:52,080
Well, I called it.
嗯，我早就说过了。

93
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:56,440
So in 2022, if we do win the World Cup, you know who said it first.
所以到2022年，如果我们真的赢了世界杯，你知道是谁先说的。

94
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,440
All right.
好的。

95
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,440
Do you have money on that?
你押注了吗？

96
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,440
Yes.
是的。

97
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,440
All right.
好的。

98
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:04,120
So apart from this, we saw some really great vocabulary in this lesson.
除了这个，我们在这节课中还看到了一些很棒的词汇。

99
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:09,840
So let's take a look at it now in Language Takeaway.
那我们现在在语言要点部分来看看它们。

100
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,840
Language Takeaway.
语言要点。

101
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,840
All right.
好的。

102
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:16,600
We've got a lot of soccer words for you, but they're all important.
我们为你准备了很多足球词汇，但它们都很重要。

103
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:19,240
So let's take a look at the first one.
那我们来看看第一个。

104
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,720
Kick off.
Kick off。

105
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,720
Kick off.
Kick off。

106
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,720
Kick off.
Kick off。

107
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,920
So a kick off.
所以kick off。

108
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:26,320
This is how you start a soccer game, right?
这是足球比赛开始的方式，对吧？

109
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,320
Right.
对。

110
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:31,240
So in the beginning, the referee blows the whistle and you kick the ball to another player.
所以一开始，裁判吹哨，你把球踢给另一个球员。

111
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,240
That's the kick off.
那就是开球。

112
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,240
OK.
好的。

113
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:36,560
So our next phrase, out of bounds.
下一个短语，out of bounds。

114
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:38,000
Out of bounds.
Out of bounds。

115
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,000
Out of bounds.
Out of bounds。

116
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,000
OK.
好的。

117
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,000
Out of bounds.
Out of bounds。

118
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,840
This is a great word.
这个词很棒。

119
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:47,960
So in soccer, when the ball goes out of bounds, it goes outside the white lines, right?
在足球中，当球出界时，它跑到白线外面了，对吧？

120
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:48,960
Right.
对。

121
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,960
Outside of the playing field.
比赛场地之外。

122
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,960
OK.
好的。

123
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:51,960
And you can use it in all other sports.
你可以在所有其他运动中使用它。

124
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,120
You can use it in basketball.
你可以在篮球中使用它。

125
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:55,160
You can use it in tennis.
你可以在网球中使用它。

126
00:04:55,160 --> 00:04:56,800
Or football or anything.
或者橄榄球或其他任何运动。

127
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,800
Right.
对。

128
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:00,560
So any part that is not for playing.
所以任何非比赛区域。

129
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,560
Out of bounds.
Out of bounds。

130
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,600
What's our next word?
下一个词是什么？

131
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,760
Throw in.
Throw in。

132
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,160
A throw in.
一个throw in。

133
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,720
A throw in.
一个throw in。

134
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,720
OK.
好的。

135
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:10,120
So a throw in.
所以throw in。

136
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:12,240
The ball goes out of bounds.
球出界了。

137
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,000
How do you put it back into play?
你怎么把它重新投入比赛？

138
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,600
Obviously, a throw in.
很明显，一个界外球。

139
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,600
OK.
好的。

140
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,960
So you throw in the ball.
所以你把球扔进来。

141
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:21,760
That's the only time where a soccer player will actually grab the ball with his hands.
这是足球运动员唯一一次用手拿球。

142
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,760
All right.
好的。

143
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:26,000
Now, another soccer term we have here, offside.
现在，我们还有另一个足球术语，offside。

144
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,000
Offside.
Offside。

145
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,000
OK.
好的。

146
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:30,720
So this is a little bit difficult to explain.
这个有点难解释。

147
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:34,040
But just imagine you're on the soccer field.
但想象一下你在足球场上。

148
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:36,480
And you are trying to score a goal.
你试图进球。

149
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,280
Now, you have some defenders, right?
现在，你有一些后卫，对吧？

150
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,280
Right.
对。

151
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:41,880
Those are the people who are trying to take the ball away.
那些是试图抢走球的人。

152
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:45,880
And you pass the ball to somebody who is behind the defenders.
你把球传给一个在后卫后面的人。

153
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:48,600
Oh, and that person is offside.
哦，那个人就越位了。

154
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,600
Exactly.
没错。

155
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:55,240
So, you must be at all times in the same position as the defenders or in front of them.
所以，你必须始终与后卫处于同一位置或在他们前面。

156
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,120
But you can't be all the way in the back.
但不能一直跑到后面。

157
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,120
OK.
好的。

158
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:01,200
So is this a noun or a verb or an adjective?
那这是名词、动词还是形容词？

159
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,280
So this is an adjective.
这是形容词。

160
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,640
He is offside.
他越位了。

161
00:06:03,640 --> 00:06:04,640
That's his condition.
那是他的状态。

162
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,640
OK.
好的。

163
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,640
Great.
很好。

164
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,640
Excellent explanation, Marco.
解释得很棒，Marco。

165
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,640
Thank you.
谢谢。

166
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:09,640
All right.
好的。

167
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:15,840
Now, we're going to look at three different phrases for three types of kicks in soccer.
现在，我们要看三个关于足球中三种踢球方式的短语。

168
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:16,840
OK.
好的。

169
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,700
So let's take a look at this.
那我们来看看这个。

170
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:20,320
The first one is goal kick.
第一个是goal kick。

171
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,320
A goal kick.
一个goal kick。

172
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,320
OK.
好的。

173
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,320
Goal kick.
Goal kick。

174
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,840
So who does the goal kick?
谁踢球门球？

175
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:29,480
It's usually the goalie or the goalkeeper who takes the goal kick.
通常是守门员或门将来踢球门球。

176
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,480
OK.
好的。

177
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,880
So when the goalie kicks the ball.
所以当门将踢球时。

178
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,880
Mm-hmm.
嗯哼。

179
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:35,160
Now, what about a corner kick?
那corner kick呢？

180
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,160
OK.
好的。

181
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:44,320
So if the team is attacking and the ball goes out of bounds in the back area near the goal,
如果进攻方把球踢到靠近球门的后场区域出界了，那么他们得到一个角球。

182
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,600
then they get a corner kick.
他们必须从球场的角落踢球。

183
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:48,160
They've got to kick the ball from the corner of the field.
这是一个进球的好机会，对吧？

184
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:51,520
This is a great chance to score a goal, isn't it?
没错。

185
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:52,520
Exactly.
是的。

186
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,520
Yes.
好的。

187
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,520
OK.
那penalty kick呢？

188
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:56,360
And what about a penalty kick?
Penalty kick。

189
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,360
Penalty kick.
Penalty kick。

190
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,360
Penalty kick.
Penalty kick。

191
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:03,520
So if a player gets fouled while he is in the area near the goal, he gets a penalty
如果一名球员在靠近球门的区域被犯规，他得到一个点球。

